UA 4910 was developed from the cross between Asgrow A4715 and DPL 3478.  Asgrow A4715 is a high-yielding, indeterminate, non-Roundup Ready commercial cultivar and was derived from the cross of A5474  (Douglas x A3127).  A5474 and A3127 were derived from (Tracy x D71-6234) x J74-122 and Williams x Essex, respectively.  Parents of Douglas were Williams and Calland.  DP 3478 is also a high yielding indeterminate commercial cultivar, but its pedigree is not available.
